* global init:
  - static global struct
  - dlopen all modules
  - and init connector config
  - default params
  - gui annotations (min max range and id for gui element)

* load pipeline config
  - module add (name inst)
  - connect (module inst connector x2)
  - param module inst param name varargs

* create nodes
  - provide interface calls node_add node_connect and allocate ids in global list on graph
  - from c callback
 (- optionally: automatically for simple cases)

* memory allocator
  - see glibc malloc + friends
  - best fit or first fit?

* roi size negotiations:
  - input to output
  - output to input
  - out of memory: cut into tiles and bisect

* graph walking
  - modules: for roi negotiations
  - modules: for node creation
  - nodes: for mem alloc
  - nodes: for command buffer filling

